import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Car } from '../api/models'; import { Service } from '../api/services'; @Component({ selector: 'app-cars', templateUrl: './cars.component.html', styleUrls: ['./cars.component.css'] }) export class CarsComponent { cars : Car[] =[]; constructor (private serv : Service){ } ngOnInit(): void { this.serv.getAllCar().subscribe((car) => { this.cars = car; }); } }
